headline: 2025: The year that the robotaxi went mainstream with Waymo leading the pack
summary: Alphabet's Waymo scaled up in 2025 and leads the American robotaxi market by far, while Baidu’s Apollo Go dominated in China. In San Francisco, Zoox, Tesla and Waymo are all revving up their offerings, though Waymo is the only one there that provides driverless rides in a widely available commercial service.
